<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Amazing Grace</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Amazing Grace, how sweet the sound
 That saved a wretch like me
 I once was lost but now I'm found
 Was blind, but now I see

[V2]
 When we've been here ten thousand years
 Bright shining as the sun
 We've no less days to sing God's praise
 Than when we've first begun

[V3]
 Amazing Grace...

[V4]
 Amazing grace, Amazing grace
 I once was lost (but now I'm found)
 And I was blind (but now I see)
 I once was lost (but now I'm found)
 And I was blind (but now I see)

[V5]
 His love is amazing
 His goodness amazing
 His salvation amazing
 All He does is amazing
 His Grace is amazing
 His forgiveness is amazing
 His victory is amazing
 His power is amazing

[V6]
 Amazing Grace...

[V7]
 Praise God, Praise God
 Praise God, Praise God...

[V8]
 Amazing Grace...

[V9]
 But now I see, but now I see
 But now I see, but now I see
 Amazing Grace!</lyrics>
<hymn_number>1922</hymn_number>
<author>Livingospel</author>
</song>